sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Knative Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS(SIMPLE)
    participant Sidecar as Istio Sidecar<br/>mTLS STRICT
    participant Caikit as Caikit Runtime<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant TGIS as TGIS Container<br/>8033/TCP gRPC (localhost)
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO Storage<br/>9000/TCP
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>openshift-user-workload-monitoring

    Note over S3,TGIS: Flow 3: Model Loading (Pod Startup)
    S3->>TGIS: KServe storage-initializer downloads<br/>model to /mnt/models/<br/>9000/TCP HTTP, AWS Key Auth
    TGIS->>TGIS: Load model from<br/>/mnt/models/artifacts/

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 1: HTTP Inference Request (caikit-tgis mode)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS(SIMPLE)
    Gateway->>Sidecar: Forward request<br/>8080/TCP mTLS
    Sidecar->>Caikit: HTTP request<br/>8080/TCP plaintext (localhost)
    Caikit->>TGIS: gRPC inference delegation<br/>8033/TCP plaintext (localhost)
    TGIS-->>Caikit: Inference result
    Caikit-->>Sidecar: HTTP response
    Sidecar-->>Gateway: mTLS response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request (caikit-tgis mode)
    Client->>Gateway: gRPC call<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS(SIMPLE)
    Gateway->>Sidecar: Forward request<br/>8085/TCP mTLS
    Sidecar->>Caikit: gRPC request (h2c)<br/>8085/TCP plaintext (localhost)
    Caikit->>TGIS: gRPC inference delegation<br/>8033/TCP plaintext (localhost)
    TGIS-->>Caikit: Inference result
    Caikit-->>Sidecar: gRPC response
    Sidecar-->>Gateway: mTLS response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Prometheus,Caikit: Flow 4: Metrics Scraping
    Prometheus->>Caikit: GET /metrics<br/>8086/TCP HTTP<br/>PERMISSIVE mTLS
    Caikit-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics
